  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p>The Everything Language Model is a Llama 2-based model with a 16k context released by Totally Not An LLM (Kai Howard). It was trained with the <a href=\"https://huggingface.co/datasets/totally-not-an-llm/EverythingLM-data-V2\" rel=\"nofollow\">EverythingLM Dataset</a> and is uncensored.</p>\n\n<h3>CLI</h3>\n\n<p><code>ollama run everythinglm</code></p>\n\n<p>Once loaded, change the context size to <code>16K</code></p>\n\n<pre><code>/set parameter num_ctx 16384\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3>API</h3>\n\n<p>Example:</p>\n\n<pre><code>curl -X POST http://localhost:11434/api/generate -d &#39;{\n  &#34;model&#34;: &#34;everythinglm&#34;,\n  &#34;prompt&#34;: &#34;Why is the sky blue?&#34;\n  &#34;options&#34;: {\n    &#34;num_ctx&#34;: 16384\n  }\n }&#39;\n</code></pre>\n\n<h2>Reference</h2>\n\n<p>13b parameters original source:\n <a href=\"https://huggingface.co/totally-not-an-llm/EverythingLM-13b-16k\" rel=\"nofollow\">Totally Not An LLM</a></p>\n\n        \n      ",
